Package uk.co.optimisticpanda.gtest.dto.propertyaccess

Interface Summary
IPropertyAccess These are used for introspection purposes.
IPropertyAccessFactory A Factory that creates new IPropertyAccess instances.
These are used by objects that extend PropertyAccessSupport such as the built in IEdits and IConditiones for introspection purposes.
 

Class Summary
PropertyAccessSupport A class that provides access to a correctly configured IPropertyAccess.
 

Exception Summary
PropertyAccessException A runtime exception that wraps checked and runtime exceptions thrown by IPropertyAccess.
